												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Cracks begin to boil across the surface of the globe. Lightning arcs out from between the cracks forming in the globe, arcing into the foreground. The globe dims slightly as the cracks begin to worsen. A surge of power erupts from within, obliterating one of the floating rocks nearby. Player reaction to the surge. The globe recovers from the surge only briefly before surging again, though not as violently as before. "
												}
