												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[WI][Giths monks][Custom/Construction/Reuse] As the Githyankis get closer to the Orb, they start assaulting and attacking the Orb. One gith will be seen climbing and deliver a massive punch that cracks the Orb. (HUM_M_Rig_CINE_Punch_MonkStyle_01)"
												}
