													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Some more flickering, then push in on eye socket of the skull as githyanki monks swarm over the exterior. Githyanki monks strike the globe barrier inside the eye socket. One strike lands hard enough to cause the globe to start to splinter. "
												}
